name: Skulls
description:
[SK Games]

Readme in main zip

In the arcade version the keybindings are off. I think it's like 3,4,E,R,D,F,C,V or something.

Buttons move left and right around the perimeter, hit both to launch off and try to collect three of the same item. Designed for a cocktail style arcade cabinet.

SK Games were Kai, Louie, Meg, Chris, Blake and Sof.
